&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS/MS in Computer Science or a related technical field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience scaling products and revenue through a high growth phase.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in B2B SaaS, telematics, or mobility platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
